La '''Volga''' ie l [[Lista di ruves de l'Europa#Ruves de l'Europa per lunghëza|ruf plu lonch de l'Europa]]. La ie dl dut te la [[Ruscia]], passa tres l [[zënter]] y l [[sud de la Ruscia]] y se jeta ite tl [[Mer Caspich]].
La Volga à na lunghëza de {{formatnum:3531}} km y n [[ciavuel idrografich]] de {{formatnum:1360000}} km²<ref name=gvr>[http://textual.ru/gvr/index.php?card=179058 «Река Волга»] {{Webarchive|url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305021422/http://textual.ru/gvr/index.php?card=179058 |date= 2016-03-05 }}, Russian State Water Registry</ref>. La ie nce l ruf de l'Europa cun la majera purteda tl delta, danter {{formatnum:8000}} y {{formatnum:8500}} m³/s. L vën udù coche l ruf nazionel de la Ruscia.<br>
Storicamënter fova l ruf n punt de ancnutenda mpurtant per plu zivilisazions europees.<ref>{{Cite book|title=Grand Strategy of the Byzantine Empire |last=Luttwak, Edward N.|date=2011|publisher=Belknap Harvard |isbn= 978-0674062078|pages=52|oclc=733913679}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last= Walker|first= Joel |date= 2007|title=Iran and Its Neighbors in Late Antiquity: Art of the Sasanian Empire (224–642 C.E.)|journal=American Journal of Archaeology|volume=1 11|issue= 4|pages= 797|doi= 10.3764/aja.111.4.795|s2cid= 192943660 |issn=0002-9114}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title=The Volga river|last=McNeese | first = Tim|date=2005|publisher=Chelsea House Publishers|isbn= 0791082474|location= Philadelphia|pages=14–16|oclc=56535045}}</ref>

